title: #92Noon! Montage/JG/Bercich/Gabe/PJ
description: Victory Monday! First hour includes Vikings takes, JG on the Gophers, a cameo by Matt Birk for more football as well! Pete Bercich calls in for next-day opinions, VEN's Gabe Henderson joins most of the final hour and PJ Fleck's weekly chat wraps the show!
